{"tid":1264074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】想扮藍絲為香港出番分力嘅唔該入嚟","createTime":"2019-06-28T13:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T17:18:25.000Z","uid":72209,"like":215,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"59f4450df384a2fef036adf09cb832996c8a0ca2","tid":1264074,"uid":72209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，因為急住要收人，所以改咗標題同少少內容出多次po！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n背景：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1263600/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1263600/page/1</a><br />\n我決定<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重整旗鼓，招兵買馬，同班五毛死過</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我希望大家都可以整多一個facebook ac，而大家只需要幫手like個facebook page，同埋互like啲留言就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFacebook班廢老藍絲好容易羊群效應，見到個page又話支持建制又多like嘅，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自己都會like埋</span></strong>，<br />\n然後，佢地見到個page啲po又多like，而啲留言都多like嘅話，佢地就會認為呢啲係建制主流意見，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最後自己都信埋</span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFacebook輿論戰，係民意其中一個決勝關鍵，你地睇下前排李力持條片，都主要係喺facebook比班五毛發揚光大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而facebook輿論戰可以幫到嘅唔單只係而家嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意</span></strong>，長遠更加有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">區議會</span></span></span></span></strong>、甚至<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">立法會實質嘅選票</span></span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明我地最大嘅優勢就係人數，點解要比班五毛食住，唔可以喺輿論戰上面<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">贏盡佢? </span></span></em></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec734752f4daf197ab280789e6ef825c02cd9fa","tid":1264074,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053865878a44a41bfa7e8a5079d24627bf7ba0b3","tid":1264074,"uid":269991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4a7305f799b3a41aac21755a89bb740f3c8885","tid":1264074,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4a171c91a584f0c22ec878fd0be3eadf77620e8","tid":1264074,"uid":72209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:37:51.000Z","msg":"今次要推爆佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893ca8673d9a12132ca438560e7361d3825050c3","tid":1264074,"uid":87600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:41:40.000Z","msg":"撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\